---
title: Middle Eastern-Spiced Beef & Pork Tacos with Capsicum Relish, Celery Slaw & Feta
description: One pan, two powerhouse flavours and three tacos. Let’s count it down! Cooking in one pan takes the fuss and bother out of
dinner so you can focus on the fun times. Two delicious additions of chermoula and chargrilled capsicum relish are perfect for spicing up tacos, three of which have your name written on them.

